snippet.title: Battle of BackYard: Trailer no1
snippet.description:
Whishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2630690/Battle_of_BackYard/

Prepare for the most explosive, fun-filled aerial combat right in your own backyard! Battle of BackYard is here, bringing together WWII-inspired model planes, over-the-top weapons, and chaotic multiplayer action.

🔔 Subscribe for more updates, gameplay, and trailers.
